        <ul>
            <li>fix bug</li>
        </ul>
        <b>1.1.2</b>
        <ul>
            <li>modify dialog size</li>
        </ul>
        <b>1.1.1</b>
        <ul>
            <li>fix bug.</li>
            <li>add option 'local variable'.</li>
        </ul>
        <b>1.1</b>
        <ul>
            <li>add the function of automatically generating code in the Java or Kotlin class.</li>
        </ul>
